/gen/schemas

# NOTE: certs/ IS committed on purpose in this repo. The Let's Encrypt
# cert for localhost.gourmelyhub.busticco.com is embedded into the
# binary via include_bytes! at compile time, so CI needs it in the
# checkout. The private key is safe to publish — see SECURITY.md
# (the domain only resolves to 127.0.0.1, there is no MITM position).
